  "text": "which is identical to the dispersion relation predicted by the paraxial wave theory [Eq. (3)], verified by experiments, and is consistent with Goosman's raybased analysis [CITATION_1] . My result demonstrates that both ray-based and wave-theory analysis methods work equally well in understanding the spectral dispersion properties of VIPAs, so that either technique can be used to design optical systems containing these devices. ",
